msgstr "Linked Discourses 45"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.62:0.2"
msgid "6. Sūriyapeyyālavagga"
msgstr "6. Abbreviated Texts on the Sun"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 62. Dutiyayonisomanasikārasampadāsutta → yoniso (pts1)
msgctxt "sn45.62:0.3"
msgid "62. Dutiyayonisomanasikārasampadāsutta"
msgstr "62. Accomplishment in Proper Attention (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.62:1.1"
msgid "“Yadidaṃ—yonisomanasikārasampadā."
msgstr "“… accomplishment in proper attention."

msgctxt "sn45.62:1.2"
msgid ""
"Yonisomanasikārasampannassetaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno pāṭikaṅkhaṃ—ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāvessati, ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkarissati."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant accomplished in proper attention can expect to develop and "
"cultivate the noble eightfold path."

msgctxt "sn45.62:1.3"
msgid ""
"Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu yonisomanasikārasampanno ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ "
"maggaṃ bhāveti, ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaroti?"
msgstr ""
"And how does a mendicant accomplished in proper attention develop and "
"cultivate the noble eightfold path?"

msgctxt "sn45.62:1.4"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sammādiṭṭhiṃ bhāveti rāgavinayapariyosānaṃ "
"dosavinayapariyosānaṃ mohavinayapariyosānaṃ … pe … sammāsamādhiṃ bhāveti "
"rāgavinayapariyosānaṃ dosavinayapariyosānaṃ mohavinayapariyosānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant develops right view, right thought, right speech, "
"right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right "
"immersion, which culminate in the removal of greed, hate, and delusion."

msgctxt "sn45.62:1.5"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu yonisomanasikārasampanno ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ "
"maggaṃ bhāveti, ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkarotī”ti."
msgstr ""
"That’s how a mendicant accomplished in proper attention develops and "
"cultivates the noble eightfold path.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.62:1.6"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.62:1.7"
msgid "Sūriyapeyyālaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.62:2.1"
msgid "Kalyāṇamittaṃ sīlañca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.62:2.2"
msgid "chando ca attasampadā;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.62:2.3"
msgid "Diṭṭhi ca appamādo ca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.62:2.4"
msgid "yoniso bhavati sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
